spec_data.Name: cegui06
spec_data.Description:
Crazy Eddie's GUI System is a free library providing windowing and widgets for
graphics APIs / engines. This package contains the older version 0.6 for
apps which cannot be easily ported to 0.7. As such this version has been build
without additional image codecs or xml parsers.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Sun 06 Aug 2017 11:31:59 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: CEGUI library 0.6 for apps which need this specific version
